<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Installation Successful - BarnabAI</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4A154B;
    }
    .success {
      background-color: #d4edda;
      border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
      color: #155724;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Installation Successful!</h1>
  <div class="success">
    <p><strong>Success!</strong> The BarnabAI Slack app has been installed in your workspace.</p>
    <% if notice %>
      <p><%= notice %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <p>You can now use BarnabAI in your Slack workspace to manage GitHub pull requests.</p>
  <p>To get started, connect your GitHub account and start a conversation in a PR thread!</p>
</body>
</html>
